hael-Kiwanuka">Michael Kiwanuka</a>和<a href="/artists/Turnstile">Turnstile</a> 。</p><p>其余阵容包括 Floating Points（现场）、Caribou、 <a href="/artists/ANHONI-and-the-Johnsons">ANHONI 和 Johnsons</a> 、 <a href="/artists/Denzel-Curry">Denzel Curry</a> 、 <a href="/artists/TV-on-the-Radio">TV on the Radio</a> 、 <a href="/artists/Wet-Leg">Wet Leg</a> 、Cap&#39;n Jazz、 <a href="/artists/Kim-Deal">Kim Deal、</a> <a href="/artsits/Los-Campesinos!">Los Campesinos！</a> 、耶稣蜥蜴、 <a href="/artists/Waxahatchee">Waxahatchee</a> 、 <a href="/artists/Fcukers">Fcukers</a> 、 <a href="/artists/Been-Stellar">Been Stellar</a> 、 <a href="/artists/Destroyer">Destroyer</a> 、 <a href="/artists/Magdalena-Bay">Magdalena Bay</a> 、 <a href="/artists/Squid">Squid</a> 、This is Lorelei、Chat Pile、 <a href="/artists/High-Vis">High Vis</a> 、 <a href="/artists/Angélica-Garcia">Angélica Garcia</a>等等。</p><p>节日的普通和 VIP 周末通行证现已发售，可<a href="https://www.primaverasound.com/en/tickets?e=primavera-sound-porto-2025-12-14-jun-2025" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>购买。 Revolut 客户可以享受节日全票 10% 的折扣，也可以通过 Kaboodle 获得付款计划。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DCEfqEosegS/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60